# apostles (according to the book of Luke 6:12-16)

0. Apostles

1. Peter (Simon)

2. Andrew

3. James the son of Zebedee

4. John the son of Zebedee

5. Philip

6. Bartholomew

7. Matthew

8. Thomas

9. James the son of Alphaeus

10. Simon the Cananite (Zelotes)

11. Judas the brother of James

12. Judas Iscariot



